---
/*
  Paper-grain overlay (design-system A.2 / C.1).
  A single fixed, decorative, aria-hidden layer that textures every non-hero
  section. One instance covers the whole page (it is position:fixed); the hero
  paints its own stronger grain within its own box. Static — no motion to
  reduce. The .gb-grain rule lives in global.css so any section/page can reuse
  the class directly without this wrapper.
*/
---
<div class="gb-grain" aria-hidden="true"></div>
